full_text:
In 2016, a security firm found some of these issues in a particular pacemaker. Instead of informing the manufacturer, they worked w/ a hedge fund to short the stock and then released their research publicly, putting ppl at risk.

The FDA issued a recall:
https://t.co/CCDWrv4Y9Z
